    "Additionally, human-annotated benchmarks were employed to provide a ground truth for evaluating the factual correctness of the model's outputs.",
    "The combination of these metrics allowed for a thorough assessment of the system's performance across multiple dimensions.",
    "Baseline and Comparison ModelsSeveral baseline models and comparison models were included in the experiments to provide a comprehensive evaluation of the proposed approach.",
    "The primary baseline model was the unaugmented Llama model, which served as the control to measure the impact of integrating the RAG mechanism.",
